<div class="meeting">
  <article>
    <h1 class="helvetica">
      <small>
        <%= content(@conn, "Meeting Type", :text) do %>
          Meeting
        <% end %>
      </small>
      <%= content(@conn, "Meeting Title", :text) do %>
        <%= @thesis_page.title %>
      <% end %>
    </h1>
    <h2 class="helvetica">
      <%= content(@conn, "Meeting Sub-heading", :text) do %>
        A birds guide to functional programming
      <% end %>
    </h2>
  </article>
  <section>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <ul>
          <li><%= content(@conn, "Time", :text, do: "Time: 7-8pm") %></li>
          <li><%= content(@conn, "Day", :text, do: "Day: Wednesday, Jan. 1, 2019") %></li>
          <li>
            <%= content(@conn, "Location", :html) do %>
              <a href="https://sandboxhawaii.org/" alt="Sandbox website">HTDC Sandbox</a>
            <% end %>
          </li>
          <li>
            <%= content(@conn, "Address", :html) do %>
              <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/643+Ilalo+St,+Honolulu,+HI+96813/@21.296994,-157.8657639,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x7c006e0f5b137809:0x5be3e1f3c9fc3d8d!8m2!3d21.296994!4d-157.8635752" alt="Sandbox map">643 Ilalo St. Honolulu, HI 96813</a>
            <% end %>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <%= content(@conn, "Event Description", :html) do %>
          <p><%= @thesis_page.description %></p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <%= content(@conn, "Meeting Image", :image, alt: "Meeting image", do: "https://place-hold.it/342x435") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h1 class="helvetica">
      <%= content(@conn, "Description Sub-Heading", :text, do: "Description Sub-heading") %>
    </h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <%= content(@conn, "Additional Description", :html) do %>
          <p>Selfies hashtag meh biodiesel keytar chillwave lomo iceland PBR&B gastropub bespoke iPhone pour-over hot chicken. Coloring book hashtag leggings 90's typewriter, tattooed flannel celiac godard freegan sartorial prism. Pork belly activated charcoal gastropub vegan air plant church-key butcher migas lyft tofu. Small batch shoreditch ugh hell of butcher put a bird on it, master cleanse deep v fashion axe iPhone edison bulb. Vape unicorn flexitarian schlitz. Art party schlitz edison bulb cliche vinyl austin fingerstache iPhone forage truffaut.</p>
          <p>Biodiesel synth selvage fixie PBR&B la croix shaman pickled copper mug sustainable vinyl readymade. Echo park sriracha vaporware single-origin coffee you probably haven't heard of them crucifix raclette four loko taiyaki tumblr health goth flexitarian chambray. Heirloom taiyaki letterpress occupy. Try-hard put a bird on it stumptown disrupt squid YOLO sriracha 3 wolf moon fanny pack cliche adaptogen sustainable pitchfork fixie snackwave.</p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
        </div>
  </section>
</div>
